## Environment Variables

Add these to your `.env` file:

```env
JWT_SECRET=your_long_random_secret
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=8h
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=your_long_random_refresh_secret
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRES_IN=7d
BCRYPT_ROUNDS=12
```

> ⚠️ Never commit `.env` files to version control.

